signature: Subscriber<? super T> call(Subscriber<? super T>)

enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve the initialization of a BoundedPriorityQueue with a specified maximum size and comparator.
The onStart method must be invoked before the call method to ensure the subscriber requests data.
The onNext method is invoked during the call method to process incoming items.
The onCompleted method is invoked after the call method to finalize the processing.
The onError method is invoked during the call method to handle any errors.
